  left: 0px;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  color: #bbb;
}
.tl-node.sel:after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 1px;
  left: 1px;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  background: #ff8000
}
.tl-arrow {
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  transform: scale(.999);
  border: 0 solid transparent
}
.tl-arrow.u {
  margin-top: -1px;
  border-width: 0 3px;
  border-bottom: 7px solid
}
.tl-arrow.u.sm {
  border-bottom: 5px solid #bbb
}
.tl-line {
  background: #bbb;
  width: 2px
}
.tl-arrow.merge {
  height: 1px;
  border-width: 2px 0
}
.tl-arrow.merge.l {
  border-right: 3px solid #bbb
}
.tl-arrow.merge.r {
  border-left: 3px solid #bbb
}
.tl-line.merge {
  width: 1px
}
.tl-arrow.cherrypick {
  height: 1px;
  border-width: 2px 0;
}
.tl-arrow.cherrypick.l {
  border-right: 3px solid #bbb;
}
.tl-arrow.cherrypick.r {
  border-left: 3px solid #bbb;
}
.tl-line.cherrypick.h {
  width: 0px;
  border-top: 1px dashed #bbb;
  border-left: 0px dashed #bbb;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0);
}
.tl-line.cherrypick.v {
  width: 0px;
  border-top: 0px dashed #bbb;
  border-left: 1px dashed #bbb;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0);
}
